  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, single center, non-randomized study to evaluate the arrhythmia
      detection performance during ventricular events.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The system will continuously monitor the patient's cardiac activity which will be compared to
      standard telemetry system.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
